<plot>This made-for-video documentary gives horror film fans a behind-the-scenes look at the making of Jeepers Creepers, a film about two siblings being chased by a demon hungry for human flesh. Also included are interviews with the cast and crew, who share their experiences from making the film and discuss some of the special efforts that went into it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?063790</url></doc>
